A conversation near me draws my attention. 'I'm sure Novus wasn't attending the Wheel,' a female voice comments. 'I don't think he would have stayed silent when they talked about him.'

'Who asked your opinion?' a man answers. I turn my head in time to see a woman look down with an ashamed expression. I barely see the man's face. What a disgusting tyrant.

