I notice my sister Gloria, walking towards the Pavilion on her own. Everyone is looking at the Wheel, except her. She pushes people aside, followed by disapproving looks. This is very strange. I was warned. 

Dinner starts right after the Wheel ends. Perhaps this is my only opportunity to try to do something about her. But if I talk to Gloria I may have another fit. 

