Shadows flicker in the doorway the man used. Figures enter our room and point rifles at us. 'Don't move.'

'Captain, there are two more here! Unarmed!'

'Caprinus, bring them here,' commands a stronger voice. 'The others, keep inspecting the cellar.'

<% if (s.cryingEndCompanion == 'Clara') {
